entries.source: Chat Edit: 'so how is the integration between AI model and local UI app doing?'

Chat Edit: 'My current workflow is the UI app (mAIware folder) using hardcoded json data and push those json to display on the UI app.
I have just added the real AI model (mAIware---AI) to the codebase. I want to integrate the real AI model with the local UI app and the server (mAIware-server):
The AI model prints out "sample_index,sample_name,sample_path,votes_benign,votes_malware,ensemble_label,ensemble_score,true_label,ensemble_class,ensemble_class_id"
If any of those is also included in the currently hardcoded local app's json, replace the hardcoded one with the AI model's one.
If the hardcoded json has any sections which the AI model's output doesn't, keep them.
If the AI model's output has any sections which the local app's json doesn't have, add those to the json and display them as new UI elements on the local app.
Tell me if there is any issues.'
